Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zabi family seeks to impose\Na dictatorship over all of humanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...ruling from the Principality of Zeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...a giant space city-state\Nfloating beyond the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.42,0:01:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to defeat this dictatorship...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Earth Federation continues\Nits stubborn resistance...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...on Earth and in space.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,...the White Base evaded an attack\Nfrom a Zeon space cruiser...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...and escaped from the space city Side 7,\Neventually landing on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.82,0:02:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,However, without a chance to contact\Nthe Federation Forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.32,0:02:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...the young crew was forced\Nto continue fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.35,0:02:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was an endless series\Nof terrifying encounters.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming Home
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? What's this? Whoa...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hee! Cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Having the sunlight shine from one place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It all seems so artificial.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:03:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...\Nthis is what they call nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.65,0:03:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true. When they talk of\Nthe infinite expanse of space...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,...I guess this is what they mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He went to see his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.05,0:03:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, was that his Core Fighter just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He said his hometown was\Nabout 30 km east of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.93,0:03:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! I feel like I've been betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.85,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's one of the elite, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everyone living on Earth\Nis part of the elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, Amuro's father lived in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Amuro has never really lived\Nwith his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just having a home on Earth\Nmakes him elite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.69,0:03:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like there were\Na lot of air strikes around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.78,0:03:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear there's guerrilla fighting here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.88,0:03:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure Mother's not Injured, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring us some booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oopsy-daisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.71,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,- This is my house.\N- What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stop it!\N- But this punk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, it's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.39,0:04:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry we entered your house\Nwithout permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No one here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an abandoned house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,An abandoned house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.19,0:04:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...? Mother, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mother!\N- He doesn't believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she died running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you don't want to be apart from Amuro,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.22,0:05:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But gong to space{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You should see the constructioni\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want Amuro to see It.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.63,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I understand that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I don't think I can...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forgive me, Amuro.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.48,0:05:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just can't get used to living In space.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, little boy?\NPlaying house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:06:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you miss your mommy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.87,0:06:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pay for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.41,0:06:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all we have to live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pay me for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.99,0:06:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pick it up!\NHave the soldier pick it up for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,- Why don't you say that again, kid?!\N- Insolent brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I said pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say, you little...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.75,0:06:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- Pick it up! Pick it up!\N- Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,- You...\N- Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell\Nwould a kid like you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.43,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If we weren't here, this town would've\Nbelonged to Zeon long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.98,0:07:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Self-important brat!\N- I remember...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy's Amuro!\NHe was a friend of my daughter's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please stop! He's just a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.83,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?! How dare you...!\N- I'll give you back your money...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...so, please go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.67,0:07:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers who survived\Nwere abandoned by headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.84,0:07:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No allies came to help them,\Nso that's how they ended up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.68,0:07:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,War is really terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... So Comilly is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not just my daughter. My husband, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Being left alive and alone is a cruel fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- You've seen your mother, right?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Didn't you get her letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother's a volunteer\Nat the refugee camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.58,0:07:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,S-She's alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the church over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The hill back there,\Nwhere you used to play with Comilly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.33,0:08:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy's completely retreated.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,With not one fighter to greet us...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.39,0:08:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...these guns will start to rust.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is part of our job, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Luggun 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All is normal in Area 304.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.11,0:08:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All hands, return to ship! Return to ship!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prepare for anti-air combat!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemies?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.87,0:08:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. There's no friendly ID signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,10 km out at sea, and approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.29,0:08:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we mobilize the White Base?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.71,0:08:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No. They'll spot us more easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be in trouble if they\Ncontact their main force.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take the initiative\Nand shoot them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Core Fighter,tions complete!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, your launch path Is clear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Core Fighter, you may launch when ready.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.47,0:09:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger! I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Something's coming!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Looks like a fighter. Damn! He's behind us!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.66,0:09:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Descend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! And they're only a patrol craft!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it. This is where Mother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey! Something's coming!\N- An airplane!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's check it out!\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, isn't that a Federation fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.58,0:10:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wow! Cool!\N- It's a real fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.93,0:10:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a soldier, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.68,0:10:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're here for...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...but could you hide that fighter right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.97,0:10:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that? I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.90,0:10:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your enemy has a forward base\Njust beyond those mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.15,0:10:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And they come around on patrol\Nonce a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.17,0:10:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy may have\Nalready detected you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can attend to your business afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I... understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.16,0:10:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro... Is it really you, Amuro...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.29,0:10:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.94,0:10:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lucky him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.42,0:11:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but can you deal with the fighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.92,0:11:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, go hide it quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.08,0:11:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll talk after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.83,0:11:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,- Is that your son?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.56,0:11:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the Zeons even attacked\Nthat backwater of a Side...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I guess we don't know if your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.95,0:11:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,More soldiers showed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.95,0:12:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.63,0:12:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? Watch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- What kind of fighter is that?\N- I don't know...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.23,0:12:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Hot Dog patrol!\NEnemy fighter sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Current position, Y-207!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.90,0:12:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Oh no! Look over there!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be leaking fuel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.76,0:13:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bright! Looks like they got my fuel tank!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The enemy craft Is damaged,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.60,0:13:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Can't you confirm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't stick around any longer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Operators, can you calculate\Nthe enemy's escape route?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can tell is that it's southwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Toward Amuro's hometown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu, can you get back to ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's no problem, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have Amuro do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla! Send Amuro an emergency sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hurry!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Everyone stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody move.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:14:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a report that an enemy fighter\Nlanded near here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid. You know anything about a plane?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell me about it,\Njust between you and me. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How would I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we're not popular here.\NHere, have some chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.20,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want it!\NGive me back my mom and dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.96,0:14:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How frightening!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.11,0:14:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost your chance to have chocolate, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.93,0:14:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.99,0:14:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How could they signal me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, what was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.89,0:14:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm turning 89 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, lady!\NWho's sleeping in the bed there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one of the injured. Nobody special...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.92,0:15:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,- He's my son! He's injured!\N- If you've got nothing to hide, then show us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.95,0:15:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro! Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.18,0:15:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to live. Call a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.77,0:15:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Even they might have children, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you aim a gun\Nat someone like that, and fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.33,0:16:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Mother, are you saying\Nthat you don't care if I get killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.12,0:16:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is war!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.66,0:16:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true, but it's not right\Nto point guns at people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.42,0:16:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother! Don't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.05,0:16:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you love me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.18,0:16:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How could a mother not love her child?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro, Is something wrong?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- No.\N- I see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have an emergency.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Zeon patrol plane is headed that way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The White Base will launch\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.08,0:16:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, I don't remember\Nbringing you up to be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please go back to the way you were!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.13,0:17:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now... we're at war!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What a disgraceful child!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.30,0:17:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they heading?\NIs there a base?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.64,0:18:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if there's a base or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.32,0:18:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! They didn't make it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry with anti-aircraft fire!\NLaunch Dopps!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Missed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.19,0:18:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gunperry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it! They brought the Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Amuro!\NWanna try a mid-air transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A mid-air transfer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's try testing it in combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't, Mr. Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't tested the docking parts\NMs. Matilda brought us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro says he wants to try it, so why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.51,0:19:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because he was raised by a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.39,0:19:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't like that as a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a boy who couldn't even kill a fly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Vertical distance, 50 meters!\NActivate docking searcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Laser searcher synchronized!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,5... 4... 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,2... 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam B Parts released!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.21,0:19:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Core Change! Docking, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, good job!\NGundam A Parts released!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn Kai!\NIt's not synchronized!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That Amuro! What is he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going after the enemy base, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point in hitting a forward base\Nin such a backwater region?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And that Kai. Docking the Gundam\Nin battle without testing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just wasting ammunition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,In our situation,\Nit's like cutting our own throats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,- Am I wrong?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want to stay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where my comrades are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.51,0:21:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be his mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking care of Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. Amuro has saved us\Non many occasions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.69,0:21:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.31,0:21:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,His work today was truly impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.31,0:21:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.66,0:21:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be leaving shortly, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.78,0:21:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.09,0:21:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.30,0:21:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,...Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:21:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.83,0:22:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We will watch over your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.88,0:22:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.13,0:23:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,White Base isn't the only unit\Nshort on weapons and ammunition.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.01,0:23:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief Cuaran's cunning attack\Non the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...is enough to bring terror\Nto Amuro and crew...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,...as they bravely fight the Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.58,0:23:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Will Amuro be able to survive the assault?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.27,0:23:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Time, Be Still.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Time, Be Still
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:23:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:54.91,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:59.91,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:10.13,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:15.05,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:19.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:25.06,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:29.65,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:39.95,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:54.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:59.91,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.91,0:24:10.13,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.13,0:24:15.05,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.05,0:24:19.68,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.68,0:24:25.06,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:29.65,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.65,0:24:39.95,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
